$$2.14 \pm 0.13$$
$$2.01 \le X_r \le 2.27$$
- Proc. 2:
$$X_{mc} = 2.153$$
$$2.15 \pm 0.07$$
$$2.08 \le X_r \le 2.22$$

c3) Medida
$$9.81$$
- Proc. 1:
$$9.81 \pm 0.13$$
$$9.68 \le X_r \le 9.94$$
